Subject: Permission Scans Not Updating Even After Successful Scans
Description: We have several servers that get scanned successfully for permissions but the data does not update in the Access Information Center.
What_We_Know__c: When logging in to the Access Information Center, the customer notices discrepancies in the data, as though the data has not been updated.
Next_Steps__c: The root cause of information discrepancies in AIC is rooted in the failed bulk import being worked on 442548 and this ticket is being closed.
Solution_Comment__c: The root cause of the information discrepancies in AIC is related to the bulk import failure, which is being addressed on ticket 442548.
